    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the game</h2>Many Kanji characters can be created by combining other Kanji characters.<br>Watch as the Kanji assembly factory automatically moves through the game!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324520/extras/427c6f3919413039c7631e0723216b4f.poster.avif?t=1705710520\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324520/extras/427c6f3919413039c7631e0723216b4f.webm?t=1705710520\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324520/extras/427c6f3919413039c7631e0723216b4f.mp4?t=1705710520\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Flow</h2>There are two modes in this game: &quot;Stage Mode&quot; and &quot;World Mode<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Introduction of Stage Mode</h2>The game progresses in stages.<br>When you start the game from the beginning, the stages are automatically generated. You can play over and over again!<br>When you complete a stage, you can choose from three different machines to get the one you want. Predict the machines you will need in the next stage and strategically collect the machines you have!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324520/extras/2dbb0db69baec4382aed4086cbd6a76c.avif?t=1705710520\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324520/extras/801ce14d91c7d7e7fa8d2a610d4843eb.avif?t=1705710520\" width=640 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Introduction to World Mode</h2>The player becomes the manager of a Kanji factory.<br>The objective is to purchase a factory site and grow the factory.<br>All machines are leased, so you must pay rental fees at regular intervals.<br>To make money, you need to sell more complex Kanji characters.<br>Make more complicated Kanji characters by increasing the number of machines that can be rented by delivering the specified Kanji characters!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324520/extras/2cc30e467a1fbf1277e8320ef003c042.avif?t=1705710520\" width=640 height=350 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324520/extras/a45404cda1dd92f833c3cbfd93b62449.avif?t=1705710520\" width=636 height=564 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to create a factory</h2>1. place the generating machine. This machine will generate the specified Kanji characters at regular intervals.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324520/extras/21ce1113b19bf8e3e8dfece7aaefc973.avif?t=1705710520\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>2. place the assembling machine. This machine takes two adjacent Kanji characters and assembles them into one Kanji character.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324520/extras/772ab0bb8749782e195d80bf1fd2b99e.avif?t=1705710520\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>3. place the delivery and redemption machines. You can clear the stage and earn money by using these machines to deliver the Kanji characters specified for each stage.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2324520/extras/09d4e0ba24989c014702ed127d0bacbb.avif?t=1705710520\" width=640 height=360 /></span>",
